      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Version-controlled simulation code and ML training scripts; documented software environment (Python 3.10, TensorFlow 2.12, Fluent 2023R1); regression test suite passing.",
      "rationale": "All CFD and ML training scripts are stored in a version-controlled repository (Git tag v1.4.2). The Conda environment specification is archived alongside the package. Fluent solver version is documented. A regression test suite covering 12 canonical flow cases and 3 surrogate smoke-tests passes without failures. SQA level meets MRL 2 requirements."
