      "rationale": "Fluent 2023R1 k-omega SST implementation verified against the NASA Turbulence Modeling Resource backstep benchmark; velocity profile agreement within 3% of reference. Hemolysis power-law source term verified against an analytical single-element test case. ML surrogate forward-pass arithmetic verified via unit tests comparing layer outputs to hand-computed values for a two-node reduced network."
