      "rationale": "CFD NIH predictions at four validation conditions are within 15% of FDA experimental data (maximum deviation 14.3% at 2500 RPM / 3 L/min). Surrogate holdout RMSE of 0.031 and MAPE of 2.8% across target operating points satisfy the ±5% criterion. Both layers of the prediction pipeline meet their respective acceptance criteria."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Relevance of the quantities of interest",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
