      "rationale": "Validation uses the FDA generic centrifugal pump — the same geometry class as the subject CPB device. Flow regimes (turbulent, Re 4,000–18,000) and rotational speeds overlap with the COU operating envelope. Fluid properties match clinical CPB conditions (hematocrit-adjusted viscosity). Validation activities are judged sufficiently relevant for MRL 2 assessment."
    },
    {
