      "acceptanceCriteria": "Physics model selection (turbulence closure, hemolysis constitutive law) justified by comparison to experimental data and literature precedent.",
      "rationale": "k-omega SST turbulence model selected based on demonstrated performance for rotating machinery internal flows in peer-reviewed literature and the FDA benchmark study. Power-law hemolysis model (Giersiepen et al. coefficients) is the standard formulation for CFD hemolysis prediction per ASTM TIR42. Model form uncertainty is acknowledged as a primary source of CFD prediction error and is bounded by the ±20% experimental comparison criterion."
    },
    {
